{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"571","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"法規趨嚴 美西碳權價格創新高","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>工商時報 顏嘉南<span lang='EN-US'> 2019.11.20</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E7%A2%B3%E6%AC%8A1.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 411px;' /></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>加州和奧勒岡州實施更嚴格低碳燃油標準，<span lang='EN-US'>9</span>月碳權價格均較兩年前翻倍。圖／美聯社</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<hr />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>美國加州和奧勒岡州政府實施更嚴格的低碳燃料標準，刺激潔淨能源投資，帶動美國西岸交通工具燃料的碳信用（<span lang='EN-US'>carbon credit</span>，又稱碳權）價格，躥升至歷史新高水準。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>根據加州政府最新公布報告顯示，加州的「低碳燃油標準」（<span lang='EN-US'>Low Carbon Fuel Standard</span>；<span lang='EN-US'>LCFS</span>）碳權價格，在<span lang='EN-US'>9</span>月和<span lang='EN-US'>10</span>月躥升至新高紀錄，價格較兩年前增加<span lang='EN-US'>1</span>倍有餘。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>此外，鄰近加州的奧勒岡州，<span lang='EN-US'>9</span>月碳權價格亦創下歷史新高，較兩年前的水準勁升將近三倍。</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: center;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;<img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E7%A2%B3%E6%AC%8A2.jpg' style='width: 600px; height: 349px;' /></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>雖然煉油和石油進口公司在過去幾年累積不少碳權，然而排碳法規一年比一年嚴苛，石油業者必須購買更多碳權，才能符合排碳量標準。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>美國生質燃料公司<span lang='EN-US'>Red Rock Biofuels</span>執行長庫萊薩（<span lang='EN-US'>Terry Kulesa</span>）表示：「如果你從事再生能源燃料銷售業務，最有利可圖的市場就在加州和奧勒岡州。」</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>加州政府<span lang='EN-US'>2018</span>年將碳權的範圍擴大至永續飛航燃油。加州表示，國際飛航市場占全球<span lang='EN-US'>2</span>％的溫室氣體排放量。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>波士頓再生燃油業者<span lang='EN-US'>World Energy</span>斥資<span lang='EN-US'>3.5</span>億美元，將位在洛杉磯外圍的煉油廠改建為生產生質燃油，因此取得美國聯合航空（<span lang='EN-US'>United Airlines</span>）自洛杉磯起飛的班機飛航生質燃料大訂單。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>World Energy</span><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>執行長吉博利斯（<span lang='EN-US'>Gene Gebolys</span>）指出：「待該煉油廠完成轉型計畫後，<span lang='EN-US'>2021</span>年底前公司在加州的投資金額將逼近<span lang='EN-US'>10</span>億美元。如果不是為了<span lang='EN-US'>LCFS</span>，公司不會有這筆開銷。」</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>根據加州政府估算，<span lang='EN-US'>2018</span>年加州碳權交易金額合計超過<span lang='EN-US'>20</span>億美元。「低碳燃油聯盟」主管諾伊斯（<span lang='EN-US'>Graham Noyes</span>）表示，隨著碳權價格攀升至紀錄新高水準，<span lang='EN-US'>2019</span>年的碳權交易金額估計將上看<span lang='EN-US'>30</span>億美元。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>資料來源<span lang='EN-US'>: https://ctee.com.tw/news/global/176833.html</span></span></p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2019-11-22","clk_count":"153"}},"__N_SSG":true}